\c 20
\s Abanye abantwana bakoIsrayeli balwa labakoBhenjamini
\p
\v 1 Khona bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli baphuma, inhlangano yonke yabuthana njengamuntu munye\x + 21.5. Josh. 22.12. 1 Sam. 10.17. 11.7,15. Dute. 13.12.\x*, kusukela eDani kusiya eBherishebha lelizwe leGileyadi\x + 18.29. 2 Sam. 3.10.\x*, eN\nd kosi\nd*ni eMizipa\x + Josh. 18.26.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo induna zabo bonke abantu, zazo zonke izizwe zakoIsrayeli, zazimisa ebandleni labantu bakaNkulunkulu\x + 1 Sam. 14.38. Isa. 19.13.\x*, izinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amane zamadoda ahamba ngenyawo, ahwatsha inkemba\x + 20.15,17,25,35,46. 8.10.\x*.
\v 3 (Abantwana bakoBhenjamini basebesizwa ukuthi abantwana bakoIsrayeli babenyukele eMizipa.) Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesithi: Tshono, lobububi benziwa njani?
\v 4 Indoda engumLevi, indoda yalowo owesifazana owayebulewe, yasiphendula yathi: Ngafika eGibeya engeyakoBhenjamini, mina lomfazi wami omncane, ukuze silale \add khona\x + 19.15.\x*\add*.
\v 5 Abahlali\x + 19.22,25,26.\x* beGibeya basebengivukela, bazingelezela indlu bemelene lami ebusuku, befuna ukungibulala, bamdlova umfazi wami omncane, waze wafa\x + Josh. 24.11.\x*.
\v 6 Ngasengimbamba umfazi wami omncane, ngamquma iziqa, ngamthumela elizweni lonke lelifa lakoIsrayeli\x + 19.29.\x*, ngoba benza amanyala lobuwula koIsrayeli\x + 19.23.\x*.
\v 7 Khangelani, lina lonke lingabantwana bakoIsrayeli, phanini ilizwi leseluleko senu lapha\x + 19.30.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Abantu bonke basebesukuma njengamuntu munye besithi: Asiyikuya, ngulowo ethenteni lakhe, njalo asiyikuphambukela, ngulowo endlini yakhe.
\v 9 Kodwa khathesi, nansi into esizayenza kuyo iGibeya. Si\add za\add*melana layo ngenkatho\x + Josh. 7.14. 14.2. 1 Sam. 10.20,21. 14.41,42. Neh. 11.1. Zaga 16.33. Jona 1.7. Seb. 1.26.\x*,
\v 10 sithathe abantu abalitshumi phakathi kwekhulu ezizweni zonke zakoIsrayeli, lekhulu phakathi kwenkulungwane, lenkulungwane phakathi kwenkulungwane ezilitshumi, ukuze bathathele abantu umphako, ukuze, nxa sebefike eGibeya koBhenjamini, benze ngokobuwula bonke ababenze koIsrayeli.
\v 11 Ngakho wonke amadoda akoIsrayeli ahlanganyela umuzi, njengamuntu munye emoya munye.
\p
\v 12 Izizwe zakoIsrayeli zasezithuma amadoda esizweni sonke sakoBhenjamini zisithi: Yibubi bani lobu obenzeke phakathi kwenu\x + Dute. 13.14. Josh. 22.13,16.\x*?
\v 13 Ngakho-ke anikeleni lawomadoda, abantwana bakaBheliyali, abaseGibeya ukuze siwabulale\x + Dute. 13.13.\x*, sisuse ububi koIsrayeli\x + Dute. 13.5.\x*. Kodwa abakoBhenjamini kabafunanga ukulalela ilizwi labafowabo, abantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 14 Kodwa abantwana bakoBhenjamini babuthana bevela emizini baya eGibeya, ukuze baphume ukuya empini labantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 15 Abantwana bakoBhenjamini basebebalwa ngalolosuku bevela emizini, amadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lesithupha\x + Nani 1.37. 26.41.\x* ahwatsha inkemba\x + 20.15,17,25,35,46. 8.10.\x*, ngaphandle kwabahlali beGibeya, ababalwa baba ngamadoda angamakhulu ayisikhombisa akhethiweyo.
\v 16 Phakathi kwabo bonke lababantu kwakulamadoda akhethiweyo angamakhulu ayisikhombisa angamanxele; wonke la ayejikijela ilitshe ngesavutha enweleni engakhuthi\x + 3.15. 1 Lan. 12.2.\x*.
\v 17 Amadoda akoIsrayeli asebalwa, ngaphandle kukaBhenjamini, amadoda azinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amane\x + 20.2. Nani 1.46. 26.51. 1 Sam. 11.8.\x* ahwatsha inkemba\x + 20.15,17,25,35,46. 8.10.\x*; wonke la ayengamadoda empi.
\p
\v 18 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesukuma benyukela eBhetheli\x + 20.26,31. 18.31.\x*, babuza uNkulunkulu bathi: Ngubani phakathi kwethu ozakwenyukela kuqala empini labantwana bakoBhenjamini\x + Nani 27.21.\x*? IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: NguJuda kuqala\x + 1.2.\x*.
\v 19 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebevuka ekuseni, bamisa inkamba maqondana leGibeya.
\v 20 Amadoda akoIsrayeli asephuma ukuya empini loBhenjamini; amadoda akoIsrayeli azihlelela ukumelana labo empini eGibeya.
\v 21 Abantwana bakoBhenjamini basebephuma eGibeya, babhubhisela emhlabathini koIsrayeli ngalolosuku amadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lambili.
\v 22 Abantu, amadoda akoIsrayeli, basebeziqinisa bahlela futhi impi kuleyondawo ababezihlelele khona ngosuku lokuqala.
\v 23 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesenyuka bakhala inyembezi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* kwaze kwahlwa. Babuza eN\nd kosi\nd*ni bathi: Ngisondele yini futhi empini ngimelane labantwana bakoBhenjamini umfowethu? IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Yenyukani limelane laye\x + 20.18,26,27.\x*.
\v 24 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesondela ebantwaneni bakoBhenjamini ngosuku lwesibili.
\v 25 UBhenjamini wasephuma eGibeya emelene labo ngosuku lwesibili, babuya babhubhisela emhlabathini ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli amadoda azinkulungwane ezilitshumi leziyisificaminwembili; bonke labo bahwatsha inkemba\x + 20.15,17,25,35,46. 8.10.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Ngakho bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli labo bonke abantu benyuka bafika eBhetheli, bakhala inyembezi bahlala lapho phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, bazila ukudla ngalolosuku kwaze kwahlwa, banikela iminikelo yokutshiswa leminikelo yokuthula phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 20.18.\x*\nd*.
\v 27 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebebuza eN\nd kosi\nd*ni (ngoba umtshokotsho wesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu wawulapho ngalezonsuku\x + Josh. 18.1. 1 Sam. 4.3,4.\x*,
\v 28 loPhinehasi indodana kaEleyazare indodana kaAroni\x + Nani 25.7. 31.6. Josh. 24.33.\x* wema phambi kwawo ngalezonsuku\x + Dute. 10.8. 18.7.\x*) besithi: Ngibuye ngiphinde yini ukuphuma impi ngimelene labantwana bakoBhenjamini umfowethu, loba ngiyekele? IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Yenyukani, ngoba kusasa ngizabanikela esandleni sakho.
\v 29 Ngakho uIsrayeli wamisa abacathami maqondana leGibeya inhlangothi zonke\x + Josh. 8.4.\x*.
\v 30 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesenyuka ukumelana labantwana bakoBhenjamini ngosuku lwesithathu, bazihlelela ukumelana leGibeya njengakwezinye izikhathi.
\v 31 Abantwana bakoBhenjamini basebephuma ukumelana labantu, badonswa besuka emzini, baqala ukutshaya ebantwini, ukubulala njengakwezinye izikhathi, emigwaqweni emikhulu, enye yazo eyenyukela eBhetheli lenye eya eGibeya emagcekeni, phose amadoda angamatshumi amathathu akoIsrayeli.
\v 32 Abantwana bakoBhenjamini basebesithi: Sebetshayiwe phambi kwethu njengakuqala\x + Josh. 8.5,6.\x*. Kodwa abantwana bakoIsrayeli bathi: Asibalekeni, sibadonse besuka emzini baye emigwaqweni emikhulu.
\v 33 Wonke amadoda akoIsrayeli asevuka endaweni zawo, azihlela eBhali-Tamari, labacathami bakoIsrayeli bavumbuluka endaweni yabo emadlelweni eGibeya.
\v 34 Kwasekusiza kuvela maqondana leGibeya amadoda akhethiweyo azinkulungwane ezilitshumi evela kuIsrayeli wonke; lempi yaba nzima. Kodwa bona babengazi ukuthi ububi buzatshaya phezu kwabo\x + 20.41. Josh. 8.14,15.\x*.
\v 35 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimtshaya uBhenjamini phambi kukaIsrayeli. Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebebhubhisa koBhenjamini amadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu lekhulu elilodwa ngalolosuku; bonke laba bahwatsha inkemba.
\p
\v 36 Abantwana bakoBhenjamini basebebona ukuthi sebetshayiwe, ngoba amadoda akoIsrayeli amdedela uBhenjamini, ngoba bethembe abacathami ababebamise maqondana leGibeya.
\v 37 Labacathami baphangisa\x + Josh. 8.19.\x* bahlasela iGibeya baqhubeka batshaya umuzi wonke ngobukhali benkemba\x + 9.33,44.\x*.
\v 38 Kwasekusiba lesiboniso esimisiweyo phakathi kwamadoda akoIsrayeli labacathami sokuthunqisa insika yentuthu enkulu evela emzini.
\v 39 Kwathi amadoda akoIsrayeli aphenduka empini, uBhenjamini waqalisa ukuwatshaya ukubulala emadodeni akoIsrayeli phose amadoda angamatshumi amathathu, ngoba bathi: Isibili atshayiwe lokutshaywa phambi kwethu njengempini yakuqala\x + 20.31,32.\x*.
\v 40 Kwathi iyezi liqalisa ukuthunqa liphuma emzini, insika yentuthu\x + 20.38.\x*, uBhenjamini enyemukula, khangela-ke ilangabi lomuzi lenyukela emazulwini\x + Josh. 8.20.\x*.
\v 41 Lapho amadoda akoIsrayeli etshibilika, amadoda akoBhenjamini atshaywa luvalo, ngoba abona ukuthi ububi sebuwehlele.
\v 42 Ngakho afulathela phambi kwamadoda akoIsrayeli esiya endleleni yenkangala; kodwa impi yawanamathela, lalabo abaphuma emizini bawabhubhisa phakathi kwabo\x + 20.45,47. Josh. 8.15,24.\x*.
\v 43 Bamhanqa uBhenjamini, baxotshana labo, babanyathelela phansi lula, kwaze kwaba maqondana leGibeya lapho okuphuma khona ilanga\x + Hlab. 22.12.\x*.
\v 44 Kwasekusiwa koBhenjamini amadoda azinkulungwane ezilitshumi leziyisificaminwembili; wonke la ayengamaqhawe.
\v 45 Basebephenduka babalekela enkangala\x + 20.45,47. Josh. 8.15,24.\x* edwaleni leRimoni\x + Josh. 15.32.\x*. Bakhothoza kibo emigwaqweni emikhulu abantu abazinkulungwane ezinhlanu, babanamathela kwaze kwaba seGideyomu, batshaya futhi kibo abantu abazinkulungwane ezimbili\x + Dute. 24.21.\x*.
\v 46 Ngakho bonke abawayo koBhenjamini mhlalokho babeyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu, amadoda ahwatsha inkemba; bonke labo babengamaqhawe\x + 20.44,45.\x*.
\v 47 Kodwa amadoda angamakhulu ayisithupha aphenduka abalekela\x + 21.13.\x* enkangala edwaleni leRimoni; ahlala edwaleni leRimoni inyanga ezine\x + 20.45,47. Josh. 8.15,24.\x*.
\v 48 Amadoda akoIsrayeli asebuyela ebantwaneni bakoBhenjamini, abatshaya ngobukhali benkemba, kusukela emzini wonke kusiya ezinyamazaneni, njalo kusiya kukho konke okwaficwayo. Layo yonke imizi abayificayo bayithungela ngomlilo.